name: BabyQuick
description: The BABYQUICK project is the first reflection-token on Polygon that reflects 7% QUICK TOKEN back to holders while providing a community based token with NFTs (10k Dragon Collection) and a Play to Burn video game by TheAman Studio soon to be released. Our mission is to facilitate the transition to a lower gas fee network while helping to diversify holdings in the crypto space while supporting the Polygon network. BABYQUICK has unique capabilities to ""auto yield"" into your public wallet address where you hold BABYQUICK and the BABYQUICK DIV token. There is no second site address to remember, no added gas fees to harvest, you just buy and hold BABYQUICK in your wallet and with the magic of smart contracts, the token is ""auto-staked"" and rewards you with QUICK based on our volume and liquidity pair on the exchange. The BABYQUICK community currently offers a faucet of Matic and BabyQuick to get brand new folks started with Polygon on Matic Main Net. NFT contests, giveaways, promotions are just a few of the events that are going on while we continue to expand and partner within the space.
